}}{{TIDTOC|switch}} ==Overview== This is an 8-port 10/100 Mbit Ethernet switch with 2 Gigabit Ethernet uplink ports.
It provides 802.3af and 802.3at PoE on the 8 Ethernet ports.
It's mountable in 10'' and 19'' racks with the help of included accessories.
Unfortunately, the Ethernet switch chipset information has been laser wiped from the chips surface.
